<lb ed="C I" n="0005a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 2</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>姚伯多等造像記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a00"/><mulu level="1" label="之一　碑陽" type="其他"/><head>之一　碑陽</head>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a01"/><p id="pI01p0005a0101">夫大道幽玄。以妙寄為宗。靈教<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沾</unclear>澤。以<note n="0005001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30308;＝虛【史】</note><app n="0005001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>寂為<note n="0005002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30355;＝所【史】</note><app n="0005002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">是</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">以</unclear>群方。而功不在
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a02"/>己。生成萬物。不以存私為　稱。故　能苞羅六合。而品類咸熙。纖介通
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a03"/>微。而感物不彫。經云。大道如　　　　　昧。而研之者明。至言若訥。而尋之
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a04"/>者<note n="0005003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30356;＝辨【史】</note><app n="0005003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">辨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30356;</rdg></app>。故真文彌梵。非高何以可宗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">李</unclear>　　耳和生。非玄教<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha">&CB07099;</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>以合空。<note n="0005004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00614;＝鬱【史】</note><app n="0005004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鬱</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00614;</rdg></app>陵<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">齊</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a05"/>禪。以致其真。當今世道。教紛群惑茲　　甚。假道亂真。群聚為媚。大道之□
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a06"/>清<app source="0005001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>唯真素。為潔練身。<note n="0005005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30357;＝剋【史】</note><app n="0005005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30357;</rdg></app>脩大道之本。　有北地姚伯多兄弟等。承帝舜之
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a07"/>苗冑。珠紫<note n="0005006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30358;＝奕【史】</note><app n="0005006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">奕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30358;</rdg></app>世。仰論士<note n="0005007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30359;＝爵【史】</note><app n="0005007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30359;</rdg></app>。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">書</unclear>不可訖。九　族雍<note n="0005008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30354;＝穆【史】</note><app n="0005008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30354;</rdg></app>。貞　素清潔。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">略</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">肅</unclear>至孝。通
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a08"/><note n="0005009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30360;＝於【史】</note><app n="0005009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30360;</rdg></app>神明。<note n="0005010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30375;＝望【史】</note><app n="0005010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30375;</rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">標</unclear><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">青</unclear>族。雅量淵廓。神心肅&CB31153;。發自天然。<note n="0005011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30361;＝雖【史】</note><app n="0005011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">雖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30361;</rdg></app>形寄時俗。超然<note n="0005012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30366;＝遠【史】</note><app n="0005012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30366;</rdg></app>敬。乃自
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a09"/><app source="0005005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30357;</rdg></app>削。內懷歡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">心</unclear>。<app source="0005009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30360;</rdg></app>大代太和廿年歲在丙子九月辛酉朔四日甲子。姚伯
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a10"/>多。伯龍。定　龍。伯養。天虎<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">等</unclear>。上為帝主。下為七祖眷屬。敬造皇老君文石
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a11"/>像一軀。<note n="0005013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30362;＝營【史】</note><app n="0005013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">營</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30362;</rdg></app>構莊飾。　極工匠之奇彫。隱起形<note n="0005014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30363;＝圖【史】</note><app n="0005014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30363;</rdg></app>。<note n="0005015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30317;＝瑍【史】</note><app n="0005015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30317;</rdg></app>若真容。現<app source="0005009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30360;</rdg></app>今世。綺錯
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a12"/>盡窮巧之剬。脩奉清顏。有若真對。非夫道協幽宗。理會亡言。焉能若此者。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a13"/><note n="0005016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB06082;＝于【史】</note><app n="0005016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06082;</rdg></app>時奉敬之徒。欽太極以興觀。信&CB31153;之賓。<app source="0005010" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30375;</rdg></app>玄門而<note n="0005017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30364;＝喪【史】</note><app n="0005017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30364;</rdg></app>偶。不勝欣躍之至。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a14"/>即而頌之。其辭曰。　　　芒芒太上。<note n="0005018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30365;＝疊【史】</note><app n="0005018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30365;</rdg></app><app source="0005018" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">疊</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30365;</rdg></app>幽微。<app source="0005009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30360;</rdg></app>矣皇老。誕精云湄。純<note n="0005019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30392;＝風【史】</note><app n="0005019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">風</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30392;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a15"/>漸<note n="0005020" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04152;＝鼓【史】</note><app n="0005020"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04152;</rdg></app>。品物沾暉。非至非成。熟啟<note n="0005021" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB17851;＝冥【史】</note><app n="0005021"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB17851;</rdg></app>機。　洸洸尹生。妙契玄理。<app source="0005012" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30366;</rdg></app>其城都。皓
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a16"/><note n="0005022" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30367;＝變【史】</note><app n="0005022"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">變</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30367;</rdg></app>素起。微言既暢。萬累都止。陳文五千。功不在己。沖<app source="0005001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>纏<note n="0005023" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30368;＝邈【史】</note><app n="0005023"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邈</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30368;</rdg></app>。如昧俞深。不
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a17"/>知其誰。像帝先人。化治西域。流波東秦。至感無其崇之者。因　既建石像。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a18"/><app source="0005014" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30363;</rdg></app><note n="0005024" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30316;＝藻【史】</note><app n="0005024"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藻</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30316;</rdg></app>靈仙。在軒雲遘。岳峙霄間。莊麗嚴飾。妙觀閑　閑。&CI0003;神儀。載揚真
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a19"/>賢。　濟濟川原。雍<app source="0005008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30354;</rdg></app>開關。俄　俄風流。君子　交<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">齊</unclear>。降生哲　人。敘此熟
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a20"/>資。清為時範。動為世師。非唯立德。　政化是妣。其妣唯何。唯政是匡。其政
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a21"/>唯何。<note n="0005025" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30370;＝柔【史】</note><app n="0005025"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">柔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30370;</rdg></app>而能<note n="0005026" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30369;＝剛【史】</note><app n="0005026"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30369;</rdg></app>。造立石像。德立彌章。唯我皇老。与日　　齊光。伯多。伯龍。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a22"/>姚定龍。姚伯養。姚天□。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">從</unclear>始供養。千載不<note n="0005027" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30371;＝忘【史】</note><app n="0005027"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">忘</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30371;</rdg></app>。壽身捨身。道<note n="0005028" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00644;＝氣【史】</note><app n="0005028"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氣</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00644;</rdg></app>將自。如此種福。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005a23"/>□□萇入天堂。子<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孫</unclear>□□後更煩昌。後人見之。供養<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">如</unclear>常。若當不信。□□</p>
</div2>
