<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b01"/><p id="pI01p0005b0101">清信梁冬姬供養
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b02"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b03"/>清信胡女焦供養
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b04"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b05"/>清信胡惡女供養
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b06"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b07"/>清信牛妙姜供養
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b08"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005b09"/>清信王<note n="0005029" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04537;＝職【史】</note><app n="0005029"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">職</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB04537;</rdg></app>女供養</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c01"/><p id="pI01p0005c0101">願造功者就。脩德者成。殖果有因。因中果生。信者善<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">終</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">從</unclear>明
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c02"/>至明。福<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">來</unclear>照果。果以<app source="0005015" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30317;</rdg></app>榮。<app source="0005001" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30308;</rdg></app>中遊<note n="0005030" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30349;＝翔【史】</note><app n="0005030"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">翔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30349;</rdg></app>。梵音希聲。神仙為友。歷
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c03"/>觀玉京。捨俗就道。貴在心精。　願星宿群<note n="0005031" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30350;＝僚【史】</note><app n="0005031"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">僚</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30350;</rdg></app>。牧守令長。以德
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c04"/>導民。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">立</unclear>條眾備。處物理均。善教既舒。民<note n="0005032" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30351;＝樂【史】</note><app n="0005032"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30351;</rdg></app>仰遵。邑景寧太。雅
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c05"/>詠日新。道能濟物。信与宜純。　坦坦原隰。仁義可親。左平右
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c06"/>大。北<note n="0005033" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30352;＝顧【史】</note><app n="0005033"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">顧</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30352;</rdg></app>頻山。眾泉合流。注<app source="0005016" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06082;</rdg></app>茲川。洸洸濟濟。仁林俠邊。<app source="0005008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">穆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30354;</rdg></app>〃
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c07"/>英儒。得生<app source="0005016" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">于</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB06082;</rdg></app>閒。神像功就。<app source="0005009" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">於</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30360;</rdg></app>茲有緣。安<app source="0005002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>仁理。不<note n="0005034" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30353;＝歪【史】</note><app n="0005034"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">歪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30353;</rdg></app>不偏。其
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c08"/>　<app source="0005014" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">圖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30363;</rdg></app>玉瑩。綺飾交連。既建岳峙。与山齊連。<note n="0005035" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30374;＝兆【史】</note><app n="0005035"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30374;</rdg></app>劫不移。往來
<lb ed="C I" n="0005c09"/>　神仙。<app source="0005002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>願成□。壽命萇延。</p>
