<lb ed="C I" n="0005f01"/><p id="pI01p0005f0101">願<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>主<note n="0005036" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30393;＝國【史】</note><app n="0005036"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">國</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30393;</rdg></app>王以□□物。敷教濟濟。休問<app source="0005012" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30366;</rdg></app>彰。邊　<note n="0005037" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30372;＝夷【史】</note><app n="0005037"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">夷</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30372;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f02"/>賓伏。<note n="0005038" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00321;＝災【史】</note><app n="0005038"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">災</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00321;</rdg></app>害自<note n="0005039" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30373;＝亡【史】</note><app n="0005039"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30373;</rdg></app>。德流<app source="0005035" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">兆</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30374;</rdg></app>庶。善瑞榛祥。民<app source="0005032" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">樂</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30351;</rdg></app>貞信。　臣
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f03"/>節忠良。道協靈應。族延未央。以道為基。与仙相　<app source="0005010" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">望</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30375;</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f04"/>願道民姚伯多。三宗五祖。七世父　　母。前亡後<note n="0005040" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30376;＝死【史】</note><app n="0005040"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">死</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30376;</rdg></app>
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f05"/>眷屬。若在三徒。速得解脫。得<app source="0005012" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">遠</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30366;</rdg></app>　　<note n="0005041" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18853;＝離【史】</note><app n="0005041"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18853;</rdg></app>囚徒幽執之
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f06"/>苦。上昇南宮神鄉之土。若更下生。侯王為父。當令伯
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f07"/>多父母兄弟。妻息大小。均心同信。尊道為主。學以萇
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f08"/>生。神仙為侶。福慶隆昌。子孫斯与。<app source="0005002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30355;</rdg></app>願<app source="0005005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30357;</rdg></app>成。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">若</unclear>□神
<lb ed="C I" n="0005f09"/>□。如此種福。功德□□□□</p>
